58
00:06:46,865 --> 00:06:48,533
Are you trying to protect that maiden?

59
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:52,329
I am trying to protect the Crown.

60
00:07:00,503 --> 00:07:02,380
OPERATING CENTER

61
